### Authentication

Will be handle by [Intacct](intacct.com), login and go to PM module.

### Success responses
HTTP status = 2xx

```
{
  data: { ... }
}
```

by convention for paginated endpoint:

```
{
  data: { items: [], meta: { count, limit, offset } }
}
```

### Error responses

HTTP status = 4xx/5xx

```
{
  {
    message: 'Error message',
    error_type: 'authentication' | 'validation' | 'internal'
  } 
}
```

* status 401 - type = 'authentication'
* status 400 - type = 'validation'
* status 5xx - type = 'internal'
